premise_source_doc_sentence: Newcastle  (  Staffs  )  Volleyball Club is an English volleyball club based in Newcastle-under-Lyme , Staffordshire , England which is affiliated with Volleyball England , with teams competing at the national level for women , men , girls and boys in all three formats of the sport - Volleyball , Sitting Volleyball and Beach Volleyball .
Volleyball is one of the sports that is played at the Summer Olympic Games in two disciplines : the traditional six-per-side indoor game , and the newer game of beach volleyball .
